room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Escape Kemah in Houston
room_description: You & your team of misfit bank robbers have hired a former employee from Escape Kemah Bank to help steal a million dollars. Your team has 60 minutes to enter and exit the room ON YOUR OWN before the police get notified! You have to make a crucial decision: take the money and run or stay a little longer & try to steal the million dollars. The choice is yours!
